playstore_details.title: HIIT Workout for Men Lite
playstore_details.description:
High-intensity interval training (HIIT), is a form of interval training, a cardiovascular exercise strategy alternating short periods of intense anaerobic exercise with less intense recovery periods. HIIT is the concept where one performs a short burst of high-intensity (or max-intensity) exercise followed by a brief low-intensity activity, repeatedly, until too exhausted to continue. 

Looking for HIIT workout apps and home workout for men? Try the best HIIT workouts app – HIIT workout for men Lite! With our body building app, you will get a better body shape fast. This body building app is definitely your best choice!

With the most effective bodybuilding home workout app, spending just a few minutes a day, you can build muscles, get lean and get toned without equipment at home. Toned arms, sculpted chest, six pack abs, all these are no longer a dream as long as you stick with our bodybuilding home workouts and make exercise a habit.

The Home Workout for Men focuses on 5 major muscle groups. eg:

* Arms workouts
* Chest workouts
* Abs workouts
* Legs workouts
* Shoulders & back workouts

Each exercise comes with animations guidance as well as detailed instructions to help you perform in the right form and get amazing results. 

All the exercises are designed by experts to ensure they're scientifically-proven to be effective. No need to go to the gym, and no need for a coach. Home Workout for Men Pro is your personal trainer to help you build muscles and lose weight at home.
